{"tid":1498520,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實可唔可以設立臨時政府and/or 設死線","createTime":"2019-08-23T12:24:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T08:51:20.000Z","uid":271475,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ff61ce561f21f7b50033f01d6f8f42cd84dfb2eb","tid":1498520,"uid":271475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T12:24:05.000Z","msg":"講真，At this point 可能容易過叫政府實現五大訴求 <br />\n因爲成立臨時政府唔使經港共批准，但係五大訴求要 。<br />\n當然，logistics好大問題，例如你去邊到籌款，建立外交關係，點樣獲得國際肯定。。。<br />\n但係靠自己去爭取，比起要靠港共say yes， 我地有大D發揮空間<br />\nAlso 你地究竟幾時肯設死線<br />\n淨係話會 &ldquo;行動升級&ldquo; 即係點升級<br />\n乜實際行動都冇講點懾港共<br />\n不如直接話港共唔即時(或9月一日)實現五大訴求，就搞臨時政府啦 <br />\n如果你地驚俾人話搞港獨，反正班三毛都係咁話我地而家搞港獨架啦，其實有乜分別"},{"pid":"669dc6c7c814e30237d84ca1d85850786a60a39b","tid":1498520,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T12:25:42.000Z","msg":"陸生提曬你"},{"pid":"fc919aad9199b92a32ab2c1c69b837094604a615","tid":1498520,"uid":229411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T08:50:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08cf2f4c27e7c638429c171d352c5717968c68ad","tid":1498520,"uid":29899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T08:51:20.000Z","msg":"日期: 2019．9．1<br />\n時間: 13:00<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">#推到有多啲高質文宣#</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#黑警還眼 #612 #721 #811 #823</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c3kZESP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc3kZESP.jpg&h=ba0a90fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k7wVcXg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk7wVcXg.jpg&h=05fc61c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YyFriWu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYyFri